both by its genotype and by the environment.}}</ref><ref name="r1">{{cite journal|vauthors=Dawkins R|title=Replicator selection and the extended phenotype|journal=Zeitschrift Fur Tierpsychologie|volume=47|issue=1|pages=61–76|date=May 1978|pmid=696023|doi=10.1111/j.1439-0310.1978.tb01823.x|author-link=Richard Dawkins}}</ref>

